{"tid":944122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7成女性愛「微胖爸爸身材」勝過肌肉　睪固酮較低竟是勝出關鍵","createTime":"2018-12-17T02:27:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T03:24:20.000Z","uid":212399,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"688381b613c2d3be1dc4d5f9290d0f26a92a548f","tid":944122,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T02:27:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3766/d3766488.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3766%2Fd3766488.jpg&h=73d312ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲70%女性更愛微胖爸爸身材。（圖／記者鄒鎮宇攝）<br />\n記者林彥臣／綜合報導<br />\n雖然流行文化普遍傳播女性更愛身材結實的肌肉男，但是健身公司調查發現指出，肉肉微胖的「爸爸身材」反而比肌肉男更吸引女性，甚至女性會以老公有肚子感到自豪。<br />\n根據Planet Fitness的研究指出，男性對於肌肉渴望的觀念，似乎已經過時了，這更有利於在觀看線上節目時喜歡多享用一些啤酒的男性，因為根據2000位女性所做的一項線上匿名問卷結果顯示，有70%的女性認為，比標準身材胖10公斤的男性更吸引人。<br />\nPlanet Fitness調查還發現，78%的女性認為微胖男對自己的皮膚更有自信，五分之四的媽媽自豪自己嫁給一個有「爸爸身材」的男人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2486/d2486393.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2486%2Fd2486393.jpg&h=cdf6f043&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲肌肉男示意圖，比起肌肉男，女性其實更愛微胖爸爸身材 。（圖／翻攝飆捍臉書）<br />\n雖然數據顯示微胖男比較有吸引力似乎很沒說服力，但實際上還是存在一些科學上的解釋，耶魯大學的人類學教授巴比斯卡斯（Richard Bribiescas）解釋，導致微胖男變胖的原因，主要是睪固酮下降引起的，這反而造就更好的免疫系統，意味著微胖男可能更長壽。<br />\n巴比斯卡斯教授還說，因為體型的關係，這會讓微胖男更傾向買寬鬆的褲子，更有助於營造對精子更有利的環境，提高生育率，因此女性在潛意識當中會認為，微胖的男人是個讓嬰兒更好的爸爸，所以讓這樣的數據呈現這樣的現象，變得有意義。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181216/1332021.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20181216%2F1332021.htm&d=t%2F78%2BODoCXm3BL3z0AU5BYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=e9f64159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181216/1332021.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8108afdbf5e2c5e03b1f137471ef11f9703a5dbc","tid":944122,"uid":57186,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T02:29:30.000Z","msg":"on9。"},{"pid":"a2aabb6d4cd943e132bff6c3c55ff1d1a15812e7","tid":944122,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T02:30:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e32c39de7f6baa564ec6be0bd28f7dfd93190103","tid":944122,"uid":25598,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T02:32:25.000Z","msg":"篇文肯定係毒撚寫"},{"pid":"0f0b1ee41bbf4c7244620bec405b0ec53fe782de","tid":944122,"uid":115525,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T02:33:40.000Z","msg":"佢個張肌肉男示意圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b12a883c60e6417e748fc391f8d2b8f530f64f16","tid":944122,"uid":167219,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T02:35:04.000Z","msg":"好似男人話鍾意少肥女咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後都係揀返瘦底"},{"pid":"435e868bb8f9bf0423e768221fa1de67bc0327c1","tid":944122,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T02:38:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a8038a2e839eee31b244fb50d2812696536e6e","tid":944122,"uid":29689,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T02:41:33.000Z","msg":"不嬲識欣賞肌肉嘅都只係得男性<br />\n話咩操大隻啲就易啲溝女純粹係因為佢地未操過<br />\n女性唔了解肌肉嘅美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a594ff2f1dd713d820e135d1d19f44a38e67178b","tid":944122,"uid":85629,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T02:43:35.000Z","msg":"文中肌肉男先叫「微胖」<br />\n呢種strong man身型先正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f57e34bf9bb55ae6ddccec7239b361322cd88680","tid":944122,"uid":141871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0f0b1ee41bbf4c7244620bec405b0ec53fe782de","tid":944122,"uid":115525,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T02:33:40.000Z","msg":"佢個張肌肉男示意圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T02: